sequenceDiagram
    participant TF as ToolsFactory + MCPToolsMerger
    participant R as MCPConfigResolver
    participant T as MCPToolsResolver
    participant C as MultiServerMCPClient
    participant S as Servidor MCP stdio (subprocesso local)

    TF->>R: resolve_for_agent / resolve_for_workflow
    R-->>T: conexoes por escopo (stdio: command, args, env)
    T->>T: consulta cache por tenant e escopo
    alt cache vazio
        T->>C: get_tools(connections)
        C->>S: spawna subprocesso e fala MCP via stdin/stdout
        S-->>C: tools publicadas
        C-->>T: lista de BaseTool
    end
    T-->>TF: tools MCP filtradas e mescladas as locais
